{"type":"message","id":"d5e07bcb","parentId":"0f045bc6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T19:20:08.975Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Qc0grR2MSPZ5uaDrSyyBzZAJ|fc_0b3a9073310625c10169cd6fe86b3481998117100142a8b8e6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-01\n\n## 量化任务续跑记录\n- T05 step1 的 `balanced / defensive` orders 重跑阻断已解除：先由 `aggressive` 打热股票分析缓存后，`paper_balanced_stock_analysis_overlay_20260330.json` 与 `paper_defensive_stock_analysis_overlay_20260330.json` 均达到 `cached_count=13 / live_count=0 / missing_count=0`，不再依赖 Tavily 实时搜索。\n- 已补齐产物：`research/reports/paper_balanced_merged_proposed_orders_20260330.csv`、`research/reports/paper_defensive_merged_proposed_orders_20260330.csv`。\n- 新诊断结论已落地到 `research/reports/t05_profile_homogenization_snapshot_20260330.md`：`balanced` 与 `defensive` 的 `smallcap_live_candidates.profile` 仍指向 `aggressive`，且 `smallcap_live_candidates.config` 同为 `config/strategy_smallcap_chip_aggressive.yaml`；当前三盘差异主要还是仓位/预算旋钮，不是真正独立的进取/均衡/防守候选源与评分门分层。\n\n## 稳定执行偏好\n- 张玲已明确：当 Tavily 额度用完时，直接改用其他搜索 skill 继续推进，不要因 Tavily 配额耗尽而中断；优先采用非 Tavily 路线（如 `claude-websearch`）。\n# 2026-04-01\n\n## 量化任务续跑记录\n- T05 step1 的 `balanced / defensive` orders 重跑阻断已解除：先由 `aggressive` 打热股票分析缓存后，`paper_balanced_stock_analysis_overlay_20260330.json` 与 `paper_defensive_stock_analysis_overlay_20260330.json` 均达到 `cached_count=13 / live_count=0 / missing_count=0`，不再依赖 Tavily 实时搜索。\n- 已补齐产物：`research/reports/paper_balanced_merged_proposed_orders_20260330.csv`、`research/reports/paper_defensive_merged_proposed_orders_20260330.csv`。\n- 新诊断结论已落地到 `research/reports/t05_profile_homogenization_snapshot_20260330.md`：`balanced` 与 `defensive` 的 `smallcap_live_candidates.profile` 仍指向 `aggressive`，且 `smallcap_live_candidates.config` 同为 `config/strategy_smallcap_chip_aggressive.yaml`；当前三盘差异主要还是仓位/预算旋钮，不是真正独立的进取/均衡/防守候选源与评分门分层。\n\n## 稳定执行偏好\n- 张玲已明确：当 Tavily 额度用完时，直接改用其他搜索 skill 继续推进，不要因 Tavily 配额耗尽而中断；优先采用非 Tavily 路线（如 `claude-websearch`）。\n\n## News-Market 新增 YINN\n- 已将富时中国三倍做多（YINN）加入早会快照：`skills/news-market/scripts/generate_morning_news_free.py` 新增 `us_etf` 分支，走 yfinance 实时行情（无需梯子）。\n- YINN 近三日收盘（Yahoo Finance 直连）：2026-03-27 $30.10 / 2026-03-30 $30.46 (+1.2%) / 2026-03-31 $32.81 (+7.7%)。\n- YINN 是 A 股小盘股情绪 3× 放大器，涨 1%≈YINN 涨 3%，是晨会进攻/防御判断的高置信度先行指标。\n\n## 控制塔 RED 告警根因与修复（2026-04-01 16:10）\n- **根因**：`run_paper_trading_sim_v1.py` 的 `load_orders()` 把 `stock_signal_tickets_live_20260401.csv` 等非 orders 文件当成 orders 文件处理——这类文件没有 `suggest_qty` 列，走 `pd.to_numeric(..., errors='coerce')` 后 `suggest_qty` 全为 NaN，再经过 `fillna(0).astype(int).abs()` 变成全 0，导致后续逻辑错乱，三盘模拟盘今日全部报错中断。\n- **修复**：`load_orders()` 入口加类型校验——若文件既无 `suggest_qty` 列也无 `ts_code` 列，直接返回空 DataFrame，不进入后续处理。同时删除冗余的 `df.empty` 重复判断。\n- **手动补跑**：aggressive / balanced / defensive / exit_dual / exit_tight 五个纸盘全部补跑 20260401，数据追到当天。\n- **结果**：profile_updates 全部 GREEN，控制塔从 RED → YELLOW（剩余 YELLOW 均为收盘后人工复核文件的正常过期，属于日终流程正常状态）。\n- **教训**：信号工单（tickets）和 orders 是两种不同格式的文件，`load_orders()` 必须做列类型校验，不能假信号文件必有 `suggest_qty`。\n\n## 微博简报修复要求与已知根因（2026-04-01 晚）\n- 张玲已明确：**微博简报只需要汇总并加以分析，不要主观筛除“你认为不是财经内容”的微博**；后续“微博财经大V每日简报”不得再先按 `is_stock_related` / “财经内容”口径过滤后再输出。\n- 已开始修复：`~/.openclaw/skills/weibo-monitor/scripts/fetch_weibo_v2.py` 中原先基于 `is_stock_related(post_text) < 1` 的跳过逻辑已删除，后续应让所有抓到的微博都进入汇总分析。\n- 这次“`财经内容 0 条`”不只是筛选口径问题；历史执行链路还出现了 `获取UID ... 失败: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: 'mcporter'`，导致每个大V被记为“今天0条, 财经0条”，这是另一条需要继续收口的真实根因。\n- 同轮还发现 `fetch_weibo_v2.py` 存在语法问题：`from __future__ import annotations` 不在文件开头，当前脚本编译会报 `SyntaxError`，后续续跑时要先修正这一点。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775071208970}}
{"type":"message","id":"512741d6","parentId":"d5e07bcb","timestamp":"2026-04-01T19:20:08.978Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_rO1pdZ2keCnpOgheSTl3WiyP|fc_0b3a9073310625c10169cd6fe86b388199bfd31fedb69ac37d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: openclaw-backup\ndescription: Backup and restore OpenClaw data. Use when user asks to create backups, set up automatic backup schedules, restore from backup, or manage backup rotation. Handles ~/.openclaw directory archiving with proper exclusions.\n---\n\n# OpenClaw Backup\n\nBackup and restore OpenClaw configuration, credentials, and workspace.\n\n## Create Backup\n\nRun the backup script:\n\n```bash\n./scripts/backup.sh [backup_dir]\n```\n\nDefault backup location: `~/openclaw-backups/`\n\nOutput: `openclaw-YYYY-MM-DD_HHMM.tar.gz`\n\n## What Gets Backed Up\n\n- `openclaw.json` — main config\n- `credentials/` — API keys, tokens\n- `agents/` — agent configs, auth profiles\n- `workspace/` — memory, SOUL.md, user files\n- `telegram/` — session data\n- `cron/` — scheduled tasks\n\n## Excluded\n\n- `completions/` — cache, regenerated automatically\n- `*.log` — logs\n\n## Setup Daily Backup with Cron\n\nUse OpenClaw cron for daily backups with notification:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"daily-backup\",\n  \"schedule\": {\"kind\": \"cron\", \"expr\": \"0 3 * * *\", \"tz\": \"UTC\"},\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Run ~/.openclaw/backup.sh and report result to user.\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"delivery\": {\"mode\": \"announce\"}\n}\n```\n\n## Restore\n\nSee [references/restore.md](references/restore.md) for step-by-step restore instructions.\n\nQuick restore:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway stop\nmv ~/.openclaw ~/.openclaw-old\ntar -xzf ~/openclaw-backups/openclaw-YYYY-MM-DD_HHMM.tar.gz -C ~\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n## Rotation\n\nScript keeps last 7 backups automatically.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775071208972}}
